{"tid":1238433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該記鳩住,我地係一個隨時要屌閪既狀態","createTime":"2019-06-17T22:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T23:00:23.000Z","uid":212336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75ff1f6ee2168628a38ead6c78d8393005ea0199","tid":1238433,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:56:44.000Z","msg":"我諗絕大多數既巴絲打同我一樣，係呢個幾星期心情大起大落，煩躁不安、前景迷茫，谷鳩住道氣，想靠打飛機發洩<br />\n<br />\n但唔該記鳩住，而家有隻爛臭老閪隨時擘大脾，等撚住我地屌到爆開，問題係隻老臭閪似擘唔擘，等我地無得發洩<br />\n<br />\n一時三刻打個飛機係可以轉換心情，但係係鳩咁射，任你更好體力射多幾次就無貨派，到要屌既時候腳仔軟，仲可以點？<br />\n<br />\n係佢夾鳩埋呢段時間，我地要裝備好自己，隨時備戰，佢一擘脾我地就扯爆旗屌撚死佢<br />\n<br />\n記住以下十六個字<br />\n<br />\n偶然一劣，無傷大雅，沉迷自瀆，影響埋牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＊<br />\n<br />\n見到好多戰友呢幾日都灰到爆，甚至唔少人都睇唔開想跟梁生行先一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望用呢段低俗既文字搏君一笑，收拾心情繼續抗戰，柒婆呢條數我地仲有排計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d197a4ac7c79977d9cc36f61c548ef5e731fb57f","tid":1238433,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:58:43.000Z","msg":"中出二百萬連發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08473d73672810b91c5cd9eb04996ee07d394105","tid":1238433,"uid":207641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d617030bb73579ae30b0beaefbbb40d384071244","tid":1238433,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}